* Standard quiz format
* Draw the interface and the normal (dashed). Randomize horizontal/vertical
* Decide whether to ask for index or speed
* Choose the two angles of the rays, and draw them.
  Make sure the angles are a minimum distance apart.
* Label the two sides of the interface as either nA/nB or vA/vB
* Choose whether you ask if one is "bigger" or "smaller"
* Find the correct answer.
* Ask the question and provide two buttons.
  

